      "rationale": "A three-level grid-convergence study was completed at three of five operating points using GCI methodology per ASME V&V 20. The remaining two points were assessed by analogy. Extrapolated discretization error on NIH is below 8% at converged points. Achieved level 3; required level 4 not met."
    },
    {
