      "rationale": "NIH is the primary COU QoI and was measured directly. However, the damage model predicts a scalar hemolysis index that is mapped to NIH through an empirical scaling factor calibrated on a different pump geometry. This indirect mapping introduces a surrogate step not fully accounted for in the relevance assessment. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
