      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry as the COU. Fluid properties match. Operating points cover the COU envelope but exclude the highest-speed transient ramp condition. Achieved level 3; gap at level 5 due to missing transient coverage."
