      "rationale": "Two turbulence models (k-omega SST and realizable k-epsilon) were compared at one operating point. Damage model sensitivity was not explored; only the Giersiepen–Wurzinger model was used. Model form uncertainty is not bounded across the full operating envelope. Achieved level 2; required level 5 represents a significant gap."
