      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ (N=2000) was performed on inlet flow, viscosity, and damage-model exponents. Geometry manufacturing tolerances and surface roughness were not included in the UQ ensemble. Sobol sensitivity indices were computed for the included parameters. Partial coverage of input space yields achieved level 3."
